---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import ConditionOrderTool from "../../components/ConditionOrderTool";
---
<BaseLayout title="条件单计算器 | 韭菜圈">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-10">
    <div class="mb-6">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-leaf">核心工具</p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold md:text-5xl">ETF/股票次日条件单计算器</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl leading-8 text-stone-700">选择行情快照或手动输入 OHLC，计算低吸价、高抛价和观察价。结果仅作为条件单辅助参考。</p>
    </div>
    <ConditionOrderTool client:load />
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
